---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/shared/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="Baptism" description="Ready to take the next step? Water baptism in Jesus' name is essential for salvation and the remission of sins.">
  <PageHero title="Baptism" image="/hero/1.jpg" />

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro">
        <h2>What is Baptism?</h2>
        <p>Water baptism by full immersion in the name of Jesus Christ is a foundational experience for every believer. As Peter declared in Acts 2:38, "Repent, and be baptized every one of you in the name of Jesus Christ for the remission of sins." Through baptism, we are buried with Christ and raised to walk in newness of life.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="scripture-highlight">
        <blockquote>
          "Repent, and be baptized every one of you in the name of Jesus Christ for the remission of sins, and ye shall receive the gift of the Holy Ghost."
          <cite>â€” Acts 2:38</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <div class="why-baptism">
        <h3>Why Get Baptized?</h3>
        <div class="reasons-grid">
          <div class="reason">
            <h4>For Remission of Sins</h4>
            <p>Baptism in Jesus' name washes away our sins and gives us a fresh start in Christ.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reason">
            <h4>In Jesus' Name</h4>
            <p>We baptize in the name of Jesus Christ, following the pattern of the early church in the book of Acts.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="reason">
            <h4>Full Immersion</h4>
            <p>Baptism represents being buried with Christ and raised to new life, symbolized through complete immersion in water.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="signup-section">
        <h2>Ready to Be Baptized?</h2>
        <p>We'd love to celebrate this step with you! Sign up and we'll reach out with next steps.</p>
        <a
          href="https://rolhenry.churchcenter.com/people/forms/1102414"
          data-open-in-church-center-modal="true"
          class="btn btn-large"
        >
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2c-5.33 4.55-8 8.48-8 11.8 0 4.98 3.8 8.2 8 8.2s8-3.22 8-8.2c0-3.32-2.67-7.25-8-11.8zm0 18c-3.35 0-6-2.57-6-6.2 0-2.34 1.95-5.44 6-9.14 4.05 3.7 6 6.79 6 9.14 0 3.63-2.65 6.2-6 6.2z"/></svg>
          Sign Up
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<script src="https://js.churchcenter.com/modal/v1"></script>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
  }

  .page-content .container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .intro h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .scripture-highlight {
    background: var(--color-navy);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .scripture-highlight blockquote {
    color: white;
    font-family: var(--font-script);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .scripture-highlight cite {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .why-baptism {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .why-baptism h3 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reasons-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .reason {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .reason h4 {
    color: var(--color-teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .reason p {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .signup-section {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .signup-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-navy);
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .signup-section > p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .btn-large {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-teal);
    color: white !important;
    padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-large:hover {
    background: var(--color-teal-dark);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
